manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: This multiple charging cable with 4 different USB connectors, including Dual Lightning ,USB-C and Micro USB connectors. Support to charger most of the mobile phones available on market. Product specification: ● Length: 180cm (6Ft) ● Material: Nylon Braided + Aluminium Alloy ● Packing: 2 × 4 in 1 Multiple Nylon Braided Multi USB Cables

Super Compatible: ● USB 2.0: Universally compatible with iPhone, USB-C & Micro devices, it has 4 different ports to USB cable for your most needs, it can charge 4 devices at the same time. ● Lightning Connector: Compatible with -iPhone 15 14 Plus/ 15 14 13 12 11 Pro Max/ 15 14 13 12 11 Pro/ 15 14 13 12 Mini/ 15 14 13 12 11/ SE/ XS Max/ XS/ XR/ X/ 8/ 8 Plus/ 7 Plus/ 7/ 6/ 6S Plus/ 5S/ 5/ iPad Air/ Air2/ Air 2013, iPad Mini 2/ 3/ 4/ 5 ● USB-C Connector: Compatible with Samsung Galaxy UItra S23 S22 S21 S20 S10 S9 S8, New Book 2015, Book Pro 2016, ChromeBook Pixel 2015, Google Nexus 6P/5X, OnePlus 2/3, Huawei P9, Lumia 950, Lumia 950 XL ,PS 5 and more. ● Micro-USB Connector: Compatible with most Android and Windows phones, tablets and many other devices including HTC / Nokia / LG / Sony / GPS / PS 4 device. Warm tips: ● The maximum total output current of Lightning port is 2.4A, USB-C port is 3.0A and Micro-USB port is 2.1A (For total, not for each end ) ● The actual charging speed is determined by the highest output that the wall charger can provide, you can charge multiple devices at the same time with a 5V/3A wall charger, particularly suitable for family or guests. ● Only Lightning Connector Support Sync Data, 480Mbps (Lightning Support Play Car).

TPE material + Bulletproof fiber core ● Multi cell phone charging cable with double-braided Nylon, longer service life and never rupture. Flexible And Durable ● The Multi USB cable using high-quality heat resistant aluminum alloys terminals to increase reliability and durability, with a 15,000+ bend lifespan could withstand a variety of daily connection needs and long-term use. Fast Charge & Data Sync ● Lightning Port Support Fast Charge 2.4A(Only iPhone port support data transfer). ● USB C Post Support Charge 3.0A. ● Micro USB Port Support 2.1A Charge.

Simplify your life with YTLUSN multi charging cable ● Streamline Your Charging Experience: Simplify your life with our 4 in 1 multi charger cable that works seamlessly with all your devices. ● Organize Your Environment: Bid farewell to cable clutter and untidy desks. Maintain a clean and organized workspace by charging multiple devices using a single cable. ● Convenient Double Pack: Whether you find yourself at home, the office, or traversing the globe, universal multi charger cable 2pack ensures that you are perpetually equipped with an indispensable charging companion.
